# Summary
Spaces in Amplitude help teams organize and collaborate on analyses, with content saved either to personal workspaces (private by default) or shared spaces. The feature is available on all plans but limited to one space for Starter plans and three spaces for Plus plans, with functionality for creating folders, moving content, and managing permissions.

